# 🌍 COVID-19 Global Trends Analysis

This project analyzes global COVID-19 trends using real-world data. It focuses on tracking the number of cases, deaths, and vaccinations across selected countries over time. The analysis includes visualizations to help communicate trends and insights effectively.

## 🎯 Project Objectives

- Import and clean COVID-19 global data
- Analyze time trends (cases, deaths, vaccinations)
- Compare metrics across countries (Kenya, USA, India)
- Visualize trends using charts
- Communicate findings in a simple and readable format

## 🧰 Tools & Libraries Used

- Python
- pandas
- matplotlib
- seaborn

## 🚀 How to Run the Project

1. Download the dataset [`owid-covid-data.csv`](https://github.com/owid/covid-19-data/tree/master/public/data).
2. Save it in the same directory as `covid_project.py`.
3. Run the script:

```bash
python covid_project.py
